            We at CotacolHunting collect none of your behavior while using our products, let alone sell or share your personal data with third parties.
        </MudText>
        <MudText Typo="Typo.body1">
            However, if you want to have your activities integrated (to know which cols you climbed, to participate in challenges, or to be listed on our leaderboards)
